_sText:
The BSP file size is 28MB.  The map is not completely optimized with nodraw textures.  I was never going to release this, but decided today to release it anyways for those who want it.

I have a dual core w/Geforce 7950, I get 90-250FPS depending where I'm looking.  I would not recommend this map if your still fighting games off with a Geforce MX440.

Standard servers will need to have the config edited to allow maps this size to download.
